snippet.title: Total War PHARAOH - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
A storm approaches... 🌊

Get ready to be transported back to the late Bronze Age and unearth Ancient Egypt - Total War: PHARAOH is out now!

TOTAL WAR: PHARAOH PRE-ORDER NOW - https://store.totalwar.com/en/total-war/total-war-pharaoh

Official Total War Store: https://store.totalwar.com/en/total-war/total-war-pharaoh
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1937780/Total_War_PHARAOH/
Any questions? Check out the FAQ: https://pharaoh.totalwar.com/news/announce-faq
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
